column2: SELECT m.cent_gal_ID as id, m.ra AS ra, m.dec AS dec, o.deVRad_r AS Re, o.nprof_r AS nprof, p.band as band, p.bin as bin, p.profMean as mean from MyDB.MyTable AS m CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra, m.dec, #) AS n JOIN photoObjAll AS o ON n.objid = o.objid JOIN PhotoProfile AS p ON n.objid = p.objid
